sentences: Joel Rundell (September 26, 1965 – August 8, 1990) was an American musician best known as one of the four original members and lead guitarist of the Louisiana-based alternative rock band Better Than Ezra.
Rundell died by suicide on August 8, 1990, nearly a year after the release of the band's first album, Surprise.
